```python
%matplotlib notebook
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot_to_notebook (time_sec, in_signal, n_samples, out_signal=None):
  plt.figure()
  plt.subplot(1,1,1)
  plt.xlabel("Time (u sec)")
  plt.grid()
  plt.plot(time_sec[:n_samples]*1e6, in_signal[:n_samples], 'y-' , linewidth = 0.5 , label = "Input Signal")
  if out_signal is not None:
    plt.plot(time_sec[:n_samples]*1e6, out_signal[:n_samples], 'g-' , linewidth = 1, label = "FIR Output")

  plt.legend()
```
